loggerName = 'Manual Entry TimePeriod Example'
	message = "onEditCellCommit.." + str(event)
	Standard.InterfaceModules.Flow.PrivateAPI.V1.Common.LogMessage(LoggerName=loggerName, message=message)
	data = self.view.custom.Data
	row = event['row']
	column = event['column']
	measureValue = data[row][column]
	value = event['value']
	message = str([measureValue,value])
	Standard.InterfaceModules.Flow.PrivateAPI.V1.Common.LogMessage(LoggerName=loggerName, message=message)
	connectionInformation = self.view.custom.ConnectionInformation
	connection = connectionInformation['Connection']
	userInformation = connectionInformation['UserInformation']
	measureValueID = measureValue['mvid']
	timeSchemeID = self.view.custom.ChartInfo.chartPeriodInfo.timeSchemeID
	measureID =  measureValue['mid']
	
	result = Standard.InterfaceModules.Flow.PrivateAPI.V1.TimePeriod.UpdateTimePeriodMeasureValue(
	Connection=connection,
	UserInformation=userInformation,
	MeasureValueID=measureValueID,
	Value=value,TimeSchemeID=timeSchemeID,
	MeasureID=measureID)
	
	message = str(result)
	Standard.InterfaceModules.Flow.PrivateAPI.V1.Common.LogMessage(LoggerName=loggerName, message=message)
	self.view.refreshBinding("custom.Data")
